name: Glitch Quilt DOS Punk X
description:
From the Glitch Quilt Bee

All squares in the quilt are hand-made by NFTerryBain and Sewn by Science.

New source squares added every day for new quilts to avoid repetition and improve quilt match.

This drop is to celebrate 500k OBJKTs on HEN as well as the MAXCAPACITY DOS Punks X Giveaway. Includes glitch squares from the DOS Punk X drop. Not associated with MAXCAPACITY. Just a fan.

Warm and toasty.
